## 🏗️ Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Users["👥 Users"]
        U1[Internal User]
        U2[External / BYOD]
    end
    subgraph IdP["🔐 Identity Provider"]
        AAD[Azure AD / Entra ID]
        OKTA[Okta]
        CA[Conditional Access Engine]
    end
    subgraph MFA["📱 MFA"]
        OV[Okta Verify]
        TOTP[TOTP / Authenticator]
        FIDO[FIDO2 / WebAuthn]
    end
    subgraph SP["🖥️ Service Provider"]
        SSP[SimpleSAMLphp]
        APP[Protected App]
    end

    U1 & U2 -->|Access request| SSP
    SSP -->|SAMLRequest| AAD & OKTA
    AAD --> CA --> MFA
    MFA -->|Satisfied| AAD
    AAD & OKTA -->|SAMLResponse| SSP
    SSP -->|Grant| APP
```

