## 🔄 SSO + MFA Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant SP as 🖥️ SP (sp.lab.local)
    participant IdP as 🔐 Azure AD / Okta
    participant MFA as 📱 MFA Authenticator
    participant CA as 🛡️ Conditional Access

    U->>SP: 1. Access protected resource
    SP->>IdP: 2. SAMLRequest (signed, HTTP-Redirect)
    IdP->>CA: 3. Evaluate policies
    CA-->>IdP: 4. MFA required
    IdP->>U: 5. Username + Password
    IdP->>MFA: 6. MFA challenge
    U->>MFA: 7. Approve / OTP
    MFA-->>IdP: 8. Satisfied ✓
    IdP->>SP: 9. SAMLResponse (signed, amr=mfa)
    SP->>U: 10. Session established ✓
```

